{"tid":1133934,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"已報警：岩岩去唱畸，比mk仔揀","createTime":"2019-05-01T12:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:19:25.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8591f856d9db3200b7331535b3f28959477531b9","tid":1133934,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:22:11.000Z","msg":"滑雪岩岩我大佬中左波 比左20蚊我<br />\n我好撚感動，於是同佢講今晚唱畸我既<br />\n於是我地一行六人 <br />\n帶晒音箱 歌詞簿同電結他去畸房<br />\n<br />\n接待處條友mk妹黎 <br />\n佢：今日公眾假期無學生優惠，計人頭<br />\n我：一個人可以唱幾耐<br />\n佢：半小<br />\n我：我地呢度有六個人<br />\n佢：唱三小<br />\n我即刻呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d煙肉腸係個口度滴晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我即刻捉鳩住佢衫領 兜巴星落佢老母西度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上黎唱k姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔撚洗串柒柒<br />\n可能佢都知驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻跑左入經理室<br />\n火撚滾 諗住陣間去警署報案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唱唱下k無啦啦比人串 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af8aad044ea21fb6b665661581f38eee76cd778","tid":1133934,"uid":136074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:24:42.000Z","msg":"小尷"},{"pid":"73c8e3384fdd0f216c8f6fd9b7b23c35aacd9197","tid":1133934,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:28:52.000Z","msg":"報警 ? 傻人發現案"},{"pid":"01333b984cc6f07d94ab60b3f01cf6f22cae3ab5","tid":1133934,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"邊個係咁負評唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5280a954e86fddf473bad44f66df30546e6b2075","tid":1133934,"uid":67329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"所以你打算講既笑話笑點係咪「唱三小」果度？ <br />\n<br />\n你好有趣啊！ 點解你咁有創意既！<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈！ 好厲害呀！"},{"pid":"dd7f1d54d63627f576908e81c2166408b06bfefb","tid":1133934,"uid":111070,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/eda/841/eda84132b8b7e67bbc7ba5f1b472d317733a0e9b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Feda%2F841%2Feda84132b8b7e67bbc7ba5f1b472d317733a0e9b_b.jpg&h=cdf35e12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cdd3118d5bcf86ad388ccefd57be6d76f681e2b","tid":1133934,"uid":72475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"如果你話去譚仔食三小"},{"pid":"9a37a90920462171298ef15a6caeb1a9e81781d1","tid":1133934,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"係台灣笑話定我唔明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4dc26ad903bb5de0acae4ba781124eccec2afe","tid":1133934,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"9a37a90920462171298ef15a6caeb1a9e81781d1","tid":1133934,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"係台灣笑話定我唔明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"真人真事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係笑話"},